</div>
<div class="devise_forms_background col-lg-6 col-md-6 col-sm-10 col-xs-12">
    <%= form_tag admin_create_account_path, :method => :get do %>
  	<h1 style="text-align:center"><%=current_user.merchant_name%></h1>
  	<h4 style="text-align:center">Create Your Merchant Account!</h4>
    <br />
    <div class="terms col-xs-12">
      <p>
        <br />Payment processing services for <b><%= current_user.merchant_name %></b> on Ski-Lines.com are
        provided by Stripe and are subject to the <a href="https://stripe.com/ca/connect-account/legal" target="_blank"> Stripe Connected Account Agreement</a>, which includes the <a href="https://stripe.com/ca/legal" target="_blank"> Stripe Terms of Service</a>
        (collectively, the “Stripe Services Agreement”). By agreeing to this agreement or continuing to operate as a Merchant on Ski-Lines.com,
